OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with showery outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain during the morning. Some sunny
OL,7,For bright spells developing in the
OL,8,Fafternoon; however, a continued risk
OL,9,Fof showers, possibly with hail and
OL,10,Fthunder. Pleasant in any sunshine, but
OL,11,Fotherwise feeling rather cool for June.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing this evening
OL,14,Fto leave late sunny spells. Cool to
OL,15,Fbegin the night under clear skies, but
OL,16,Ftemperatures rebounding slightly as
OL,17,Fcloud builds during the early hours of
OL,18,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
