OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA wet and windy day as rain
OL,6,Fspreads across the region, turning
OL,7,Flocally heavy at times. Feeling muggy
OL,8,Funder widespread cloud cover. Drier by
OL,9,Fthe evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,12,Fcloudy and breezy on Friday with
OL,13,Fpatchy rain. Becoming drier and warmer
OL,14,Fover the weekend as high pressure
OL,15,Fbuilds, with winds also easing and
OL,16,Fsome sunny spells at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
